The '''Repugnant spectre''' is a [[superior]] variant of the normal [[deviant spectre]]. It has a chance of spawning after purchasing the unlock ''Bigger and Badder'' for 150 [[Slayer reward point]]s from any [[Slayer master]]. They are found exclusively within the [[Catacombs of Kourend]].

